{
  "stem": "3928.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I has absolutely no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But see, it's-- a lot of time, it's very hard to put yourself on somebody else's position.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Like, I know a case when the headquarters put in a well-known Jewish leader.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I can't remember his name because I wasn't involved in this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they wanted to know all kind of information regarding you know, their connections and everything about it, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Told him, either you speak and give away these people, you know, who are doing certain things, or who are in the underground, or-- or did certain acts against the Germans or the Hungarian Arrow Cross people, or we deport your family to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, what would you do, as a man?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, I'm just asking you a logical question.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You-- you know, I am a married man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I have five children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If somebody would tell me this question, what would you say?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "What would I have said?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I love my family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Would you cooperate with them, with the hope that you save your family?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Or you don't give a darn about your family?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Now, it's a very interesting question, this, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I seen this happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I seen this happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the people talked to save their family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't know-- by the way, I don't know if they really saved this, their families.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were told they will be saved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Eichmann and his people-- they were very good in this, you know, doing all this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But again, I never seen Eichmann do anything personally, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the man who gave the orders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But personally, I never seen him personally do anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
